content: Wow the best vr experience I've ever seen. It was even scarier than ghost trains in theme parks
Brillilant I thought it was well done.
Truly amazing, love the experience would like to see what the tenticals are attached to in the cave!more dinos please!
The music is nice and eerie but the rest is only so so... Especially the graphics are of very low quality. Not particularly scary either. One or two nice ideas, that's it though.

This is the BEST VR I have seen yet!  I loved it. It made me jump, it was full of surprises, and I even screamed a couple of times. Great Job and kudos to the ones that designed it.  I will watch this again and again.  Keep them coming.

Pretty good, but too predictable due to the haunted house setup. More surprise elements, like in "Sisters", would make it scarier. Have the giant spiders jump onto the raft, not a lame clown trying to look scary in the distance.

Brilliant. Very creative and thoughtful, and longer than the usual on-rails experience. Loved the falling pillar, large scale structural stuff falling looks so cool in VR, would love to see an app with more of this. Also, a full-on demented gory version of this would be a blast. Well done, awesome work!
Just excellent ......need to update more scaring material
